#

Coconut Curry Shrimp with Cauliflower Rice and Zucchini Noodles

$15
450 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

shellfishcoconut

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freedairy-freelow-carb

Tags:

seafoodcurryhealthyquick meal

Description

A vibrant and flavorful dish featuring succulent shrimp simmered in a creamy coconut curry sauce, served over a bed of light cauliflower rice and fresh zucchini noodles.

Ingredients

  • Shrimp: 1 lb
  • Coconut milk: 1 can (14 oz)
  • Curry paste: 2 tbsp
  • Cauliflower rice: 2 cups
  • Zucchini: 2 medium
  • Garlic: 3 cloves
  • Ginger: 1 inch piece
  • Lime juice: 2 tbsp
  • Cilantro: 1/4 cup
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
